      "updated": 1,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "scenario_busy_user.yaml\n──────────────────────\npersona: \"Busy professional,\n  provides all info upfront\"\ngoal: Complete booking in < 4 turns\nassertions:\n  - booking confirmed\n  - no hallucinated dates\n  - tone is warm and professional\n──────────────────────\nScored 0-5 per assertion\nWeighted avg ≥ threshold (default 3.0)\nHallucination score ≥ 4 → auto-fail",
      "fontSize": 12,
      "fontFamily": 1,
      "textAlign": "center",
      "verticalAlign": "middle",
      "containerId": "e8",
      "originalText": "scenario_busy_user.yaml\n──────────────────────\npersona: \"Busy professional,\n  provides all info upfront\"\ngoal: Complete booking in < 4 turns\nassertions:\n  - booking confirmed\n  - no hallucinated dates\n  - tone is warm and professional\n──────────────────────\nScored 0-5 per assertion\nWeighted avg ≥ threshold (default 3.0)\nHallucination score ≥ 4 → auto-fail",
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
